Package: Rcess
Type: Package
Title: Rcess: An R package for calculating estimates of costs and economies of scale and scope
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Liang-Cheng", "Zhang", email = "liang.leon.c.z@gmail.com", role = "cre"),
    person("Liang-Cheng", "Zhang", email = "liang.leon.c.z@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Lj Stats", email = "liang.leon.c.z@gmail.com", role = "cph")
    )
Description: This package utilize the theory of economies  of  scale  and  scope  (developed by Baumol, Panzar, & Willig (1982))to calculate the average output costs, economies of scale, and economiece of scope for  different  types  of  multi-output production  industries. So far, this package can reproduce the estimates using FFCQ-M cost function (see Zhang, Worthington, and Hu (in press) for details)
